
## API v1
GET    /status                               V1::API#status
GET    /authcheck                            V1::API#authcheck

POST   /share                                V1::API#share
POST   /generate                             V1::API#generate

POST   /create                               V1::API#create

POST   /secret/:key                          V1::API#show_secret

GET    /private/recent                       V1::API#show_metadata_recent
GET    /metadata/recent                      V1::API#show_metadata_recent

GET    /private/:key                         V1::API#show_metadata
POST   /private/:key                         V1::API#show_metadata
GET    /metadata/:key                        V1::API#show_metadata
POST   /metadata/:key                        V1::API#show_metadata

POST   /private/:key/burn                    V1::API#burn_secret
